headline: Never Thought The Quality Of Coca-Cola's Earnings Was All That Good
summary: Consensus estimates expect Coke to print $0.52 in EPS, $10.68 billion in revenue and $2.67 billion in operating income, for expected y-o-y growth of +6%, -2% and +5%.
